      "body": "<!--e57a25ab6845829454e8d69fc972939a-->\n\nThe following sections might be updated with supplementary metadata relevant to reviewers and maintainers.\n\n<!--021abf342d371248e50ceaed478a90ca-->\n### Reviews\nSee [the guideline](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#code-review) for information on the review process.\nA summary of reviews will appear here.\n<!--5faf32d7da4f0f540f40219e4f7537a3-->\n### LLM Linter (✨ experimental)\n\n\n\nPossible places where comparison-specific test macros should replace generic comparisons:\n\n- [test/functional/rpc_psbt.py] `assert decoded_psbt[\"tx\"][\"locktime\"] <= block_height` -> replace with `assert_greater_than_or_equal(block_height, decoded_psbt[\"tx\"][\"locktime\"])`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert locktime > 0, f\"...{locktime}...\"` -> replace with `assert_greater_than(locktime, 0)`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert locktime <= block_height, f\"...{locktime}...{block_height}...\"` -> replace with `assert_greater_than_or_equal(block_height, locktime)`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert locktime >= block_height - 100, f\"...{locktime}...{block_height}...\"` -> replace with `assert_greater_than_or_equal(locktime, block_height - 100)`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert decoded['tx']['locktime'] == explicit_locktime, \\ ...` -> replace with `assert_equal(decoded['tx']['locktime'], explicit_locktime)`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert locktime > 0, f\"...{locktime}...\"` -> replace with `assert_greater_than(locktime, 0)`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert locktime <= block_height, f\"...{locktime}...{block_height}...\"` -> replace with `assert_greater_than_or_equal(block_height, locktime)`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert locktime >= block_height - 100, f\"...{locktime}...{block_height}...\"` -> replace with `assert_greater_than_or_equal(locktime, block_height - 100)`\n- [test/functional/wallet_create_tx.py] `assert tx.nLockTime == explicit_locktime, \\ ...` -> replace with `assert_equal(tx.nLockTime, explicit_locktime)`\n\n\n\n<sup>2026-04-06 22:36:12</sup>\n",
